OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScotland's work from home  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fguidance to be relaxed next
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fweek                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Guidance urging people to work from    
OL,6, home wherever possible in Scotland is  
OL,7, to be relaxed in favour of a "hybrid"  
OL,8, system of office and remote working.   
OL,10,FEmployers have been asked to phase     
OL,11,Fworkers back into spending some time in
OL,12,Fthe office from Monday 31 January.     
OL,14,FFirst Minister Nicola Sturgeon said the
OL,15,Fmove was possible due to a             
OL,16,F"significant" fall in Covid-19 cases.  
OL,18,FBut she warned that a "mass return" to 
OL,19,Foffices overnight could run the risk of
OL,20,Fpushing infection levels up again.     
